name: Kanagathara Exporters
overview:
Sri Kanagathara Exporters is a sole proprietorship firm that came into existence in the year 2012.

Our Product Range: Coconut Products, Green Vegetables, Root Vegetables, Fresh Coconuts, Maize Seed, Salted Snacks, Cavendish Banana, Fresh Vegetables, Indian Spice and Castor Oils.

Infrastructural Set-Up: We boast of highly sophisticated infrastructural set-up, fitted with all requisite amenities. It consists of departments such as production, quality control, warehousing and packaging others, which helps us in the execution of systematic business operations.

Our Team: Our company has the support of highly experienced and dedicated professionals, who are familiar in their respective field and deliver best products in the market.

Our Quality Assurance: Our products’ quality is always praised by clients as a result we have become the foremost choice of a huge clientele. It is just an outcome of our skillful execution, intelligent direction and sincere efforts. Apart from this, strict quality measures and guiding principles are adopted by us, which helps us in ensuring clients that offered range is in strict compliance to prescribed standards of industry.

Why Us?: Being a prominent name of industry, our company has established desired position in the industry by providing desired products to clients. With the support of our advanced infrastructural set-up and dexterous professional, we have been able to efficiently cater to the specific requirements of clients and have become their prime choice.
